channel.title: Stars By SpaghettiSauce [My first track]
channel.description:
I recently saw some people posting their first song that they made on Auxy. I decided that I should try to do the same. My first song turned out to be a really nice sounding loop, which I added on to and created a full fledged song. The song is called "stars". Hope you like it!
https://soundcloud.com/madman-52/stars
